Class EntitiesDatabaseImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • control.viewcomunication.translation.EntitiesDatabaseImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntitiesDatabase

    public class EntitiesDatabaseImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements EntitiesDatabase
    Implementation of EntityDatabase interface with a map that associates to each entity code an element of view's enumeration Entities. This enum is used to determinate the view's representation of the entity
